{"tid":2215395,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"引基本法：無人可凌駕司法獨立","createTime":"2020-09-24T03:16:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T04:27:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"82497bf1c88e18cfba6db8bf9f69d097aa59dc4b","tid":2215395,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T03:16:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/QMWMFP4A5NH6NFKQA3USA4DWLA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FQMWMFP4A5NH6NFKQA3USA4DWLA%2F&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFF%2BSpyvFQ8bIEt1ajTFSrzY%3D&h=5e92fb12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FQMWMFP4A5NH6NFKQA3USA4DWLA%2F&h=d7630a72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/QMWMFP4A5NH6NFKQA3USA4DWLA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n引基本法：無人可凌駕司法獨立<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Hj3rc70qLnv8CcOUfDCzRuhSnx4=/720x598/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RWH6WKTLPZBBDPLNXV2FDHRBYU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHj3rc70qLnv8CcOUfDCzRuhSnx4%3D%2F720x598%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRWH6WKTLPZBBDPLNXV2FDHRBYU.jpg&h=6fd5ef55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■林鄭月娥早前指香港無三權分立令社會譁然。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】特首林鄭月娥早前發表「香港並無三權分立」論，強調行政、立法和司法機關互相配合和制衡，但要經特首向中央負責。終審法院首席法官馬道立昨罕有發聲明，再三引述《基本法》多條條文，列明香港享有獨立司法權，不受任何干涉，無人可凌駕其上。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：罕有發14頁聲明  馬道立反擊左報「司法機構不容政治化」<br />\n<br />\n馬道立在聲明第一部份香港司法原則，。。。。。。。，「不受任何干涉，確保所有人在法律面前一律平等，無人可凌駕其上」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「反駁官員無三權分立論」<br />\n<br />\n港大法律學院首席講師張達明指，馬道立的聲明恰當地回應近日港府官員有關「三權分立」言論，強調司法獨立重要性，相信馬道立是擔心部份官員的言論，尤其是特首有超然地位、三權皆對特首負責，或會令公眾混淆，忽略司法獨立重要性。<br />\n<br />\n資深大律師梁家傑認為，馬道立就原則部份重新列舉《基本法》相關條文，是相當直接地再次確立司法的自主及獨立地位，。。。。。。。。。，「讓大家明白香港司法嘅獨立、自主，係受到《基本法》憲制嘅保障」，避免有人誤信不正確言論。<br />\n<br />\n特首辦回應本報查詢指，特首已多次公開表明她本人及特區政府均十分重視法治和司法獨立。《基本法》為香港特別行政區訂下行政主導的政治體制，並同時確保香港司法獨立，兩者並無衝突。"},{"pid":"bca05216aecbc96314ae2bcbdd51b6dd46b1b0a1","tid":2215395,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T03:17:39.000Z","msg":"馬道立咁強調獨立"},{"pid":"d204f75f27cfa10f395a28283c0ba901335584e7","tid":2215395,"uid":1977,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T03:19:18.000Z","msg":"香港享有獨立司法權，不受任何干涉，無人可凌駕其上。<br />\n<br />\n除左共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"912a2d41a2535f1cb2a4d1db6d577b6e0c3f632d","tid":2215395,"uid":122167,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T03:19:42.000Z","msg":"睇錯馬獨立"},{"pid":"16a593bc7e41162de117ba3e965f7b1d3fda79dd","tid":2215395,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T03:21:49.000Z","msg":"中國畜牲唔係人"},{"pid":"d38c2db8e4b15692c4d17f9bbab64dbeca41413a","tid":2215395,"uid":282064,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T03:21:51.000Z","msg":"香港中聯辦張曉明：特首地位超然於三權- BBC News 中文<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/china/2015/09/150912_hongkong_zhangxiaoming_powers\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchina%2F2015%2F09%2F150912_hongkong_zhangxiaoming_powers&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFF%2BSpyvFQ8bIEt1ajTFSrzY%3D&h=a3b89c81\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchina%2F2015%2F09%2F150912_hongkong_zhangxiaoming_powers&h=fae43c53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/china/2015/09/150912_hongkong_zhangxiaoming_powers</a>"},{"pid":"92fdd5f8b1fe72644f682ab748f751d83a5c2e56","tid":2215395,"uid":300782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T03:23:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b1542fc2c7dd9c8905a9e6b5ad5cc346009d2e1","tid":2215395,"uid":60539,"